Jinchuan locates in the west of Sichuan.

38
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,220
It's just a small area.

39
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,880
There is no need for all this.

40
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,970
Now that our army has
suffered successive defeats...

41
00:03:42,970 --> 00:03:44,300
and a great loss of morale,

42
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:46,870
I suggest that we
retreat and recuperate...

43
