56
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:32,380
I think you're getting muddled
as you get older!

57
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,150
Let me ask all of you,

58
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:44,760
who can replace Ne Qin?

59
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,260
All of you...

60
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:54,560
are my high-ranking officials...

61
