71
00:05:25,570 --> 00:05:27,480
He's secretly connived with
adherents of the former dynasty.

72
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,800
Our army has suffered defeats,

73
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,740
with grave casualties and
a great loss of morale.

74
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,080
Even Zhang Guang Si who's familiar
with the Southwest's topographic...

75
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:37,010
has suffered successive defeats.

76
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:39,390
You mustn't act recklessly.

77
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,200
Fuheng,

78
00:05:42,850 --> 00:05:43,970
can you do it?

79
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:46,300
I'm willing to go to Jinchuan now,

80
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:49,310
even if it costs me my life.

81
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,990
Young Mistress, no!

82
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:53,960
-No!
-Let go!

83
00:05:54,050 --> 00:05:57,159
Help...

84
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,370
Don't try to stop me!

85
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,560
Young Master,
Young Mistress got agitated...

86
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,880
from hearing that
you're going to Jinchuan.

87
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,720
She said it's better for her to die now...

88
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,280
rather than seeing you seek your doom!

89
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:08,040
-Let go of me!
-Young Master, please stop Young Mistress!

90
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:10,240
Young Master...

91
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,070
-Let go!
-Say it.

92
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,490
What do you want?

93
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,080
Fu Heng,

94
00:06:26,910 --> 00:06:28,590
are you even human?

95
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,740
I'm worried about you.

96
00:06:31,990 --> 00:06:33,620
But you show no concern.

97
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,400
You're worried about me?

98
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,060
No.

99
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:44,760
You're afraid that if
I die on the battlefield,

100
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,320
you'll become a widow...

101
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:49,130
and the fame and wealth that you own...

102
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,890
will all be gone.

103
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,520
What are you saying?

104
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,690
What?

105
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,020
Am I wrong?

106
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,840
I'll cut off your hand...

107
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:07,100
-Young Mistress.
-so that you can't go to the battlefield!

108
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,720
Young Mistress!

109
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,310
Young Mistress.

110
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:12,330
Leave!

111
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,730
Fu Heng,

112
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,500
don't go too far.

113
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,740
I did all this for you.

114
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,130
Is it really for me...

115
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,240
or for yourself?

116
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:32,150
You know it very well.

117
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:38,140
Go ahead if you want to get yourself
killed on the battlefield!

118
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,320
You must let me go.

119
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,159
Er Qing, listen here.

120
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,950
I hope you will remember...

121
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,880
what I'm going to say.

122
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,480
I spared your life...

123
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:56,130
not because of
the imperial heir in your womb,

124
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,760
but because I felt guilty.

125
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,620
This sense of guilt...

126
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:04,850
once drove me to do
my utmost to treat you well.

127
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,080
But what you've done...

128
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:10,920
has made me lose all my patience.

129
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,830
From now on,

130
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:17,390
be obedient and stay in this room.

131
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,240
If you dare step out of it...

132
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,760
What will you do?

133
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:30,000
If you step out with your left foot,

134
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,530
I'll cut off your left foot.

135
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:34,409
If you step out with your right foot,

136
00:08:34,409 --> 00:08:35,960
I'll cut off your right foot.

137
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,909
You're insane!

138
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,760
You dared not question His Majesty...

139
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,510
but you're insulting me here!

140
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,860
I was His Majesty's
study partner for ten years.

141
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,560
I know his character...

142
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,090
a hundred times better than you.

143
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:54,620
Even if you're extraordinarily beautiful,

144
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,620
as long as you're married to me...

145
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,440
and have become
a member of the Fuca family,

146
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:02,200
