148
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:09,300
I'm able to guess it without thinking.

149
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:15,770
You'd better pray that I return safely.

150
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,120
If I'm unable to return...

151
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,410
What if you don't return?

152
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:26,370
The Buddhist nunnery
on the outskirts of capital...

153
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:28,850
