157
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:00,440
I heard that our army
has suffered huge casualties.

158
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,280
No one in the imperial court
dares go there.

159
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:04,750
It's so dangerous for you to go there.

160
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,040
Qing Lian.

161
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:12,020
I'm sorry, Young Master.
I'm being a blabbermouth.

162
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,520
But Old Mistress has fallen sick
from worrying about you.

163
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:19,920
She said if you insist on going there,
she won't see you again.

164
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,050
If I dare not risk my life...

165
00:10:25,050 --> 00:10:26,190
and fight battles,

166
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,920
what's the point of
reading military texts...

167
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,450
and serving as an official?

168
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:34,240
I can only show my worth
on the battlefield.

169
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:35,840
Otherwise,

170
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,640
I'll feel shame...

171
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:40,930
even if I'm granted with a high salary.

172
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,640
If Old Mistress asks again, tell her...

173
00:10:46,010 --> 00:10:48,410
that I'll do what I want.

174
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,280
May she forgive me.

175
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,480
It's very risky on the battlefield.

176
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,400
What if...

177
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,130
Young Master,

178
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,780
think about Old Mistress.

179
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,520
She already lost Her Majesty.

180
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:02,020
She can't lose you either.

181
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:11,280
