♫ Who will compensate me for
the lost good prospects in this life? ♫

203
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,590
Greetings, Mother.

204
00:13:38,680 --> 00:13:40,020
Get up.

205
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,360
Have a seat.

206
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:49,480
Mother, you asked me to come here.

207
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,470
Do you have something to say?

208
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:54,640
Go get the Guilingji prescription.

209
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,670
Yes.

210
00:14:03,280 --> 00:14:07,320
This prescription is named Guiling...

211
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:10,320
which means longevity.

212
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:13,980
